# Summary
This documentation page details the integration between Amplitude and Split, allowing users to export Amplitude cohorts to Split for use in feature flag targeting and segmentation. The setup process requires collecting API keys and IDs from Split, configuring the connection in Amplitude, and then syncing cohorts with a limit of 100,000 users.

